            <div class="title">
                Minister Of Production (Duties)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1942-03-12/debates/6e8e61ed-5f39-42a6-89a5-d9bb07b13d3a/BusinessOfTheHouse" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
